title: Six Degrees of Separation (1993) 1080p AC3 HDTV OAR no logos
description:
This is my own rip.

I tried to adjust the color to match the DVD, but the HDTV broadcast had blown-out highlights, so I could only do so much.  For HD plus great color, we're going to have to wait for a Blu-Ray release.
